<br>
- Identify mob with Golden Rod of Spamminess (target the mob you want to charm, then use the effect of the rod of insidious glamour to <br>
laserpointer' it - chanters only, of course, sorry bards)<br>
- Let group know you are about to charm said mob.<br>
- Charm mob. <br>
- Target another mob. (some chanters like to attack a 'free' mob, but I find that too confusing for the rest of the group, so my charmees generally assist the tank)<br>
- pet attack (or /pet kill)<br>
<br>
&lt;/ul&gt;<br>
Ahhh, I get it- you want to retarget your pett so you can recharm it, right? The bard song charms and uncharms it every tick or something?<br>
